import os
import pydicom

path = "D:\desktop\DICOM\ST000000\SE000001"
dirs = os.listdir(path)
#if not os.path.splitext(path)[1]:
for path in dirs:
    data = pydicom.dcmread("D:\desktop\DICOM\ST000000\SE000001\\"+path, force = True)
    plt.imshow(data.pixel_array, cmap = 'gray')
    plt.show();
    print("Discription: ", str(data[0x0008, 0x0016])[53:])
    print("StudyDate: ", data['StudyDate'].value)
    print("patient Name: ", data["PatientName"].value)
    print("patient ID: ", data["PatientID"].value)
    print("Modality: ", data['Modality'].value)
    print("Manufacturer: ", data['Manufacturer'].value)
    print("ImageSize: ", data['Rows'].value, ' x ', data['Columns'].value)
    print("Sample Per Pixel: ", data['SamplesPerPixel'].value)
